Javascript Function:
    <script>....</script> uptill now anonymous block 
    -we will write a name block code. which can be call as an when it is required. 
        i.e Function use for reusability of code.
    -It is use for managing the code in the project.

    syntax:
        function fun_name(arg1,arg2..argn)
        {
            return       //if your fuction is returning the value.
        }
    e.g function addtwo(n1,n2)
        {
            retun n1+n2;
        }
        sum=addtwo(5,7);  //while using return we need to use catch value(sum)//
        document.write(sum); //printing it on the screen//
        console.log(sum);   //we use inspect and see it on console tab of browser//

